    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and retaining its original factory luster. Engineered for the discerning collector who demands uncompromising mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection, this unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a flagship vehicle in its most optimal state. Full documentation of its rigorous maintenance history is available for professional review.",
      "price": 48250.0,
