      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical pedigree is documented: the dual-VANOS system has been fully rebuilt, rod bearings replaced with VAC coated bearings, and the rear subframe reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates to eliminate chassis fatigue. The suspension geometry remains true with fresh OE bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque vectoring. This is a zero-fault, turn-key investment for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and structural integrity.",
